# Hormone Models

## SCOPE vs STOP
<font size="3">
- <b>Outcomes: </b> Prolactin, hPL, GH2, Insulin, HOME-IR, glucose (all outcomes log-transformed) <br />
- <b>Independent variables:</b> Study, GDM_new, BMI, Ethnicity (Caucasian/non-Caucasian), smoking (yes/no), GA at sampling <br />
- <b>Model fitted:</b> LME or GEE model <br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;log(hormones) ~ Study + GA at sampling + Study:GA at sampling<br />
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Random intercepts for Study ID and Plate
</font>
